292
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:37,200
Itu beruntung,
dan tak setiap saat bisa begitu.

293
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,400
Valerio.

294
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:43,480
Ada yang ingin kau ceritakan?

295
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,680
Datanglah malam ini.

296
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:51,080
Napi hukuman mati pun
bisa menikmati...

297
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:53,880
